[React recommends using `onAllReady` for crawlers](https://react.dev/reference/react-dom/server/renderToPipeableStream#waiting-for-all-content-to-load-for-crawlers-and-static-generation), like SEO crawlers, logically, but this new behaviour injects scripts and hidden HTML elements, impacting negatively in SEO scores.

