2. The modal content should always be on top of the backdrop
3. The button should always be behind the modal backdrop
4. The visual hierarchy should be maintained during the entire transition

The layering should work the same way as when `createPortal` is not used - smooth animations with proper visual hierarchy maintained throughout the transition.

